        {
            "title": "聖保羅書院學生身亡 疑校友發起聯署促交代 維護校譽讓大眾安心",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"聖保羅書院學生身亡 疑校友發起聯署促交代 維護校譽讓大眾安心\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/203781cae3a42384d229da8670bdb0df/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250309/_2025030922313522500.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">聖保羅書院學生身亡 疑校友發起聯署促交代 維護校譽讓大眾安心</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>聖保羅書院日前有一名學生在杭州交流期間身亡，教育局局長蔡若蓮表示調查已經成成，該學生離世的事件與交流及考察活動無關，惟尊重家屬意願，不披露個案內容。網上今日（9日）流傳一封題為《要求聖保羅書院公開透明交代杭州交流事件調查結果》的聯署，對象是聖保羅書院學生或舊生。\n\n</p>\n<p>聯署要求校方「以負責任、公開透明的方式處理此事」，「向公眾完整交代調查結果」，包括「事件的詳細經過與調查結果」、「學校在事件發生前後的應對措施」、「未來如何確保學生外訪安全，以防止類似悲劇發生」。發起聯署人士「期望學校展現負責任的態度，以維護校譽並讓社會大眾安心。」\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/society/3435516/%E8%81%96%E4%BF%9D%E7%BE%85%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9D%AD%E5%B7%9E%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81%E4%BA%A1-%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%A5%E8%93%AE%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E8%88%87%E8%80%83%E5%AF%9F%E5%9C%98%E7%84%A1%E9%97%9C-%E6%A0%A1%E8%91%A3%E6%9C%83%E7%B1%B2%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E9%9A%B1%E7%A7%81\">聖保羅書院學生杭州交流亡 蔡若蓮：調查證實與考察團無關 校董會籲尊重隱私</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128354/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"聖保羅書院。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a2ea7f1ef53199660f399aaa67648a8f/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_115032346_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        聖保羅書院。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/society/3433507/%E8%81%96%E4%BF%9D%E7%BE%85%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9D%AD%E5%B7%9E%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81%E4%BA%A1-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%94%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8A%E5%90%8A%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA-%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%99%95%E5%B7%B2%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E8%99%95%E7%90%86\" target=\"_blank\">聖保羅書院學生杭州交流亡 消息：中五生上吊自殺 入境處：已聯絡家屬協助處理</a>\n</p>\n<p>網上早前亦傳流一封聖保羅書院校董會主席鄭卓生致師生函，批評部分媒體和社交帖文，對這位學生的不幸離世加以不準確、具惡意的報道和討論，這些揣測和煽動讓人難過，指言論不負責任，為學生家長、學校相關人士帶來不安，亦造成困擾，呼籲大眾尊重其家人的隱私和情緒。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057224/即時-港聞-聖保羅書院學生身亡-疑校友發起聯署促交代-維護校譽讓大眾安心",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-09 22:36:06",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "遊台注意︱西門町爆街頭互斬  3少年中多刀全身浴血",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"救護人員在現場為中刀少年急救。爆料公社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3876ed5b703c46d25a4352794a61753b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250309/_2025030922255819357.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">救護人員在現場為中刀少年急救。爆料公社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>台灣台北常有港人流連的西門町，周日晚發生如電影《古惑仔》般的街頭斬人案，3名15至17歲少年身中多刀送院。\n\n</p><h2>持開山刀互砍</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多輛警車趕抵現場調查街道斬人案。爆料公社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/276a2eb003b2e691a3e50fc065e86d04/2025-03/4545456.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多輛警車趕抵現場調查街道斬人案。爆料公社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多輛警車趕抵現場調查街道斬人案。爆料公社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/22ff2bf1fd76d9b25529d4f02a578887/2025-03/20250309003102.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多輛警車趕抵現場調查街道斬人案。爆料公社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<p>據中時新聞網報道，現場為台北市漢中街50巷口，今天（9日）晚間7時許，警方獲報該地點有嚴重糾紛，當警消趕抵現場，發現有多人受傷，救護車立即幫傷者包紮止血，目前了解現場有3人少年都有多處刀傷，都已經由救護車送往醫院救治，詳細爭吵原因還有待警方釐清中。\n\n</p>\n<p>網路上有網友表示，事發當時很多人手持開山刀，從獅子林附近沿路追砍，人超級多，然後沿路罵髒話叫囂，當時在旁邊看到都快嚇死了，被砍的到處亂跑亂逃。\n\n</p>\n<p>據了解，現場當時有多人發生嚴重糾紛，警方到達現場發現有3名少年都有刀傷的狀況，其中17歲少年右手臂刀傷，15歲少年肩部、腰部多處刀傷，17歲少年左右大腿都有刀傷，三人在送醫時都意識清楚，由於今天是星期假日，當時附近有很多店家目擊，警方已經調閱附近監視器，已鎖定犯案兇嫌，將積極緝捕到案。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057223/即時-中國-遊台注意︱西門町爆街頭互斬-3少年中多刀全身浴血",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-09 22:31:14",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "朗天峰單日連沽5伙 呎價高見1.35萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"朗天峰單日連沽5伙，呎價高見1.35萬。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7613be94baa55e5de77b728a645448ca/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250309/_2025030922203054585.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">朗天峰單日連沽5伙，呎價高見1.35萬。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>嘉里發展的元朗全新盤朗天峰成交持續，今日再錄5宗成交。今日成交單位戶型涵蓋1房連開放式廚房及2房連開放式廚房單位，面積286至403方呎，成交價介乎381萬至505萬元，呎價介乎12,070至13,505元。\n\n</p>\n<p>上述成交單位包括2座21樓C室，面積403方呎，屬2房戶開放式廚房設計，以505.37萬元成交，呎價12,540元。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057222/即時-地產-朗天峰單日連沽5伙-呎價高見1-35萬",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-09 22:26:21",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "奪命提示丨張振朗拍攝時爆眉撞走黑氣望好運帶旺劇集 劉穎鏇與陳山聰對打雙手腫大一個碼 受傷仍死頂紥住蹦帶繼續打",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/4c403991b4d83b73fa0bc5674500f531/2025-03/cats_30.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/a0454b42fcee71efb1a65014c1ca0102/ae38bcfe56524278b94f5c9e1ec89761-d4b4623f435897eb84880b557561ab9d-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67cda3eadcfdc\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67cda3eadcfdf\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"張振朗和劉穎鏇今日（9日）到荃灣出席新劇《奪命提示》宣傳活動。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/bf03a0fe7580a9bf37be6cfaaa74347a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250309/_2025030921460262698.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">張振朗和劉穎鏇今日（9日）到荃灣出席新劇《奪命提示》宣傳活動。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p><br/>\n陳山聰、張振朗、劉佩玥、劉穎鏇及郭柏妍等今日（9日）到荃灣出席新劇《奪命提示》宣傳活動，張振朗指劇集等到他成為雙料視帝後出街，望好運能帶旺劇集，又表示劉穎鏇也做得非常好，更睇好對方能做視后。\n\n</p><h2>劉穎鏇 : 從未試過受那麼多傷</h2>\n<p>對於有「地獄黑仔王」之稱的振朗拍此劇時因撞爆眉骨要入院縫7針，他笑言撞完後撞走黑氣變鴻運當頭，而自己也成長不少，學識日後再拍打戲時要安全地搏命。劉穎鏇則指劇中造型上有很多突破，在打鬥方面也從未試過受那麼多傷：「成身同手嘅瘀痕，返公司要遮，因為唔連戲。最傷係同山聰打嗰場，雖然山聰衫入面攝晒Pad，但唔知點解我每次都打中冇Pad嘅位，雙手腫到大咗一個碼。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128309/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\" 劉穎鏇在劇中有泳照造型。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5e0db432cbbefa0593270ee9541345eb/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0096.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n       劉穎鏇在劇中有泳照造型。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128310/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉穎鏇看回自己的片段也忍不住笑。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/407b01b012ee941a8072cad8c99c27b2/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0097.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      劉穎鏇看回自己的片段也忍不住笑。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128311/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"跟陳山聰對打的一場戲。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d0bb884b6dfbc64abb3c62eb01f59791/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0098.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      跟陳山聰對打的一場戲。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128312/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"張振朗表示劉穎鏇做得非常好，更睇好對方能做視后。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8dcea839d02dbb714812591de21961fc/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0101.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      張振朗表示劉穎鏇做得非常好，更睇好對方能做視后。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128313/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"當張振朗被安排劉佩玥、劉穎鏇及郭柏妍圍住影相，振朗即臉紅指要「請食飯」。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/86808467d856114fdc5b495fb003e51d/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0103.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      當張振朗被安排劉佩玥、劉穎鏇及郭柏妍圍住影相，振朗即臉紅指要「請食飯」。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128314/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"張振朗指劇集等到他成為雙料視帝後出街，望好運能帶旺劇集。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9fe32349abb5b616626c5339c49f1d21/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0124.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      張振朗指劇集等到他成為雙料視帝後出街，望好運能帶旺劇集。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128315/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\" 對於有「地獄黑仔王」之稱的振朗拍此劇時因撞爆眉骨要入院縫7針。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3732ab2a74bbfcb4f170e7a6020bb313/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0125.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n       對於有「地獄黑仔王」之稱的振朗拍此劇時因撞爆眉骨要入院縫7針。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128316/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"振朗亦笑指第一場戲就已和劉穎鏇一起拗柴。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5117100f57ecbb86ca06f0b6c25b6964/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0126.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      振朗亦笑指第一場戲就已和劉穎鏇一起拗柴。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128317/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"但因之後仍要拍攝，所以兩人唯有死頂紥住蹦帶打。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b4875a8fa41cfa73757b3af9476504ab/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0127.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      但因之後仍要拍攝，所以兩人唯有死頂紥住蹦帶打。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128318/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉穎鏇則指劇中造型上有很多突破\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2645dd87de0017381d54a3d0bf94933c/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0128.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      劉穎鏇則指劇中造型上有很多突破\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128319/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉穎鏇說在打鬥方面也從未試過受那麼多傷。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cd1829bdd609e037dd68a084acd3979f/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0129.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      劉穎鏇說在打鬥方面也從未試過受那麼多傷。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128320/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"三人在活動上大騷長腿。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e4484d69a6aeb4b60e3680d2ad372fc1/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0132.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      三人在活動上大騷長腿。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128321/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉穎鏇笑言已習慣帶著運動繃帶，振朗就指日後轉行可幫紮蹦帶。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6e364402b077293cd0b0f2ef76caf348/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0140.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      劉穎鏇笑言已習慣帶著運動繃帶，振朗就指日後轉行可幫紮蹦帶。\n    </div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>振朗笑言可轉行幫紮蹦帶</h2>\n<p>振朗亦笑指第一場戲就已和劉穎鏇一起拗柴，但因之後仍要拍攝，所以兩人唯有死頂紥住蹦帶打，劉穎鏇更笑言已習慣帶著運動繃帶，振朗就指日後轉行可幫紮蹦帶。另外，振朗女友楊偲泳早前在社交網站貼出身穿背心的相，然後寫着「角色限定 售完即止」，振朗就留言表示「我買」，問他是否在宣示主權，他笑說：「唔使，主權大家都知，我好低調！」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
